1. Do NOT start implementing any features mentioned in the call record
2. Make sure to ask the user clarifying questions before creating the call record
3. **DO NOT automatically create a Notion page** - only create a Markdown file in Notion-flavored Markdown format
4. Only use the Notion MCP `notion-create-pages` tool if the user explicitly requests creating a Notion page
